msgid ""
"Secure your Quarkus application endpoints by combining xref:security-built-"
"in-authentication.adoc#basic-auth[Quarkus built-in basic HTTP "
"authentication] with the JPA identity provider to enable role-based access "
"control (RBAC).\n"
